{"tid":2403891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.21 8.31]無業女子涉塗污紅磡多處地方被捕　警方指內容別有用心","createTime":"2021-02-11T11:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T11:05:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dca3d13f039d585d240ebb83a337c1ae9e88dac6","tid":2403891,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575334-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575334-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=be3d353e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575334-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dd1885dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575334-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方以刑事毀壞罪拘捕一名57歲報稱無業的女子，涉嫌塗污紅磡區內多處地方，正被扣查。警方說留意到塗污的內容別有用心，警方過去已作多次澄清，但有人仍故意散播訊息，挑起事端，破壞社會和諧。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，本月初收到多宗投訴，指有人在紅磡區內惡意塗污，寫上「7.21」及「8.31」的字句。警方今日在馬頭圍道作便衣巡邏，發現一名女子在8處地方，用筆塗污包括垃圾筒及燈柱等位置，警方在她身上檢獲4支塗污工具，事後再發現多20地方懷疑被塗污。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7.21 8.31邊個挑起事端，邊個破壞社會和諧?"},{"pid":"ca6408f6a2bbd16082ce1a12a553a48740061558","tid":2403891,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9v0vMG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9v0vMG.png&h=65364301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n★支那好治癒gif貼圖區！（10）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2393089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2393089</a><br />\n<br />\n無尾bear快入"}]}